        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.3: \"Whole cell patch-clamp recordings of synaptic currents in beta3 -/-\ncortical neurons.\"\n- \"the weighted time constant resulting from the double-exponential\nfitting of the mIPSCs decay (Tw) was 2.5-fold larger in the beta3\n+/_ than in beta3 -/- neurons (Fig. 3).\". Experimental description: \"3-subunit-deficient mice were produced at the University of Pittsburgh\"" ;
